Complementary effects of HDAC inhibitor 4-PB on gap junction communication and 
cellular export mechanisms support restoration of chemosensitivity of PDAC 
cells.

Ammerpohl O(1), Trauzold A, Schniewind B, Griep U, Pilarsky C, Grutzmann R, 
Saeger HD, Janssen O, Sipos B, Kloppel G, Kalthoff H.

Author information:
